sequenceDiagram
    participant APP as Linux App
    participant RPMSG as rpmsg
    participant SHM as Shared Memory
    participant RTOS as RTOS IPC Task
    APP->>RPMSG: write(fd, msg)
    RPMSG->>SHM: Copy to TX vring
    SHM->>RTOS: Doorbell IRQ
    RTOS->>SHM: Read from vring
    RTOS->>RTOS: Process message
    RTOS->>SHM: Write response
    SHM->>RPMSG: Doorbell IRQ
    RPMSG->>SHM: Read from RX vring
    RPMSG-->>APP: return to read()
    Note over RPMSG,SHM: Virtio-based ring buffers
